### 所有请求都带上uid参数,并且header中带上 Authorization:token
### role 系统角色,super_admin(超管), manager(工作室), operator(运营)


### 1️⃣ 用户登录
POST {{url}}/app/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test_user",
  "password": "securepassword"
}


### 1️⃣ 创建用户
@url = http://localhost:8895
POST {{url}}/app/user/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test_user",
  "phone": "13812345678",
  "password": "securepassword",
  "role": "super_admin",
  "rate": 0.05
}

### 2️⃣ 获取用户信息
GET {{url}}/app/user/get?uid=?

