### 3️⃣ 更新用户信息
PUT {{url}}/app/user/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "updated_user",
  "phone": "13887654321",
  "rate": 0.1
}

### 4️⃣ 删除用户
DELETE {{url}}/app/user/delete?uid=1

### 5️⃣ 获取用户列表 (分页)
GET {{url}}/app/user/list?page=1&size=10

